Package models

Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.Person
  • public class Person
extends java.lang.Object
    A collection of data describing a single person in their family tree in the Family Map Application. This could represent a deceased person, a current user of Family Map, or just someone who was present during an Event.

        Creates a Person by defining each property directly
        Parameters:
        personID - is the Person ID to use
        associatedUsername - is the username of the User to tie to this person
        firstName - is the person's first name
        lastName - is the person's last name
        gender - is the person's gender: "f" or "m"
        fatherID - is the Person ID to use as this person's father (can be null)
        motherID - is the Person ID to use as this person's mother (can be null)
        spouseID - is the Person ID to use as this person's spouse (can be null)
